---
title: Salmon Florentine with Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto and Buttered Rice
description: If you love a good Florentine, you are in luck! Tender and buttery salmon takes center stage with a dreamy sun-dried tomato cream sauce with spinach and a side of sautéed sweet bell peppers.

